text.section:
The subdivisions enumerated in this subsection may adopt ordinances or resolutions supplementing this subheading. This includes the authority to regulate possession or consumption of any alcoholic beverage on any public property, property used by the public in general, or on any highway:
Anne Arundel County;
Baltimore City;
Baltimore County;
Caroline County;
Cecil County;
Charles County;
Frederick County;
Garrett County;
Harford County;
Prince George's County; and
St. Mary's County.
